gemini_1.5_Flash: WITH LucasSuperheroes AS (   SELECT     s.gender_id,     g.gender   FROM superhero s   JOIN gender g ON s.gender_id = g.id   JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id   WHERE     p.publisher_name = 'George Lucas' ) SELECT   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN gender = 'Female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS female_percentage FROM LucasSuperheroes;
chatgpt_4mini: WITH total_george_lucas AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_heroes FROM superhero s JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id WHERE p.publisher_name = 'George Lucas' ), female_george_lucas AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS female_heroes FROM superhero s JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id JOIN gender g ON s.gender_id = g.id WHERE p.publisher_name = 'George Lucas' AND g.gender = 'Female' ) SELECT ROUND((fg.female_heroes * 100.0 / tg.total_heroes), 2) AS percentage_female_superheroes FROM total_george_lucas tg, female_george_lucas fg;

gemini_1.5_Flash: WITH GoodHeroes AS (   SELECT     COUNT(CASE WHEN s.alignment_id = (       SELECT         id       FROM alignment       WHERE         alignment = 'Good'     ) THEN s.id ELSE NULL END) AS good_heroes_count   FROM superhero AS s   JOIN publisher AS p     ON s.publisher_id = p.id   WHERE     p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' ), TotalHeroes AS (   SELECT     COUNT(*) AS total_heroes_count   FROM superhero AS s   JOIN publisher AS p     ON s.publisher_id = p.id   WHERE     p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' ) SELECT   CAST(gh.good_heroes_count AS REAL) * 100 / th.total_heroes_count AS percentage_of_good_heroes FROM GoodHeroes AS gh JOIN TotalHeroes AS th;
chatgpt_4mini: WITH total_marvel AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_heroes FROM superhero s JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id WHERE p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' ), good_marvel AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS good_heroes FROM superhero s JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id JOIN alignment a ON s.alignment_id = a.id WHERE p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' AND a.alignment = 'Good' ) SELECT ROUND((gm.good_heroes * 100.0 / tm.total_heroes), 2) AS percentage_good_superheroes FROM total_marvel tm, good_marvel gm;
